BUSINESS MODEL
==============

The original Thoughts & Time project offers:

**Free Tier (Self-Hosted)**:
- Open source code under AGPL-3.0
- Run PocketBase on your own infrastructure
- No usage limits, complete data control

**Paid Tier (Hosted Service)**:
- We manage Supabase infrastructure
- 1-week free trial, then starting at $1/month
- Automatic backups, cross-device sync, premium support

Both tiers use the same AGPL-3.0 licensed code. The paid tier charges for convenience
and infrastructure, not for the software itself.

